						<h6><a role="button" class="collapsed" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseone" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseone">Anal Sex
								<span class="accor-open"><i class="fa fa-plus" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
